<br>
I'm looking for a gift to buy my girlfriend, who I'm moving in with next week.<br>
<br>
My girlfriend is a lvl60 Chanter in a good high level guild, mostly 60's raids ToV, VP, Trak and Kunark Dragons weekly, RoF and other Luclin stuff, she wears mostly SS/Thur Armor with Cha/ Int/ HP mixed stuff on other slots with Epic and she is currently using a Ry'gorr Oracle Cloak (bleh) and a Shaded Shield (she doesn't like the pulsing shield look).<br>
<br>
