<br>
Frostweaver Cloak?<br>
Heiro Cloak?<br>
Ice Burrower?<br>
Other? Resists? Int/Cha/HP combo?<br>
<br>
Orb of Infinite Void?<br>
Ry'gorr Oracle Shield?<br>
Insignia Protector?<br>
Other? Resists? Int/Cha/HP combo?<br>
<br>
Please post stats and info on drops also if you know.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your help.<br>
